---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '~/lib/siteConfig'

const updated = '2026-06-19'
---

<BaseLayout title={`Disclaimer — ${SITE_CONFIG.name}`} description={`What ${SITE_CONFIG.name} is and isn't.`}>
  <header class="container-prose page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">{SITE_CONFIG.name}</a> / <a href="/legal/">Legal</a> / Disclaimer</p>
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
  </header>

  <article class="container-prose prose">
    <p>
      Everything on {SITE_CONFIG.origin} is published in good faith for general
      information only. Use it at your own risk.
    </p>

    <div class="callout">
      <h2>SEBI disclaimer (calculators are not investment advice)</h2>
      <p>
        {SITE_CONFIG.name} is <strong>not</strong> registered with the Securities
        and Exchange Board of India (SEBI), the Insurance Regulatory and Development
        Authority of India (IRDAI), the Reserve Bank of India (RBI), or any other
        financial regulator. Nothing on this site constitutes investment, tax,
        or insurance advice under the SEBI (Investment Advisers) Regulations, 2013
        or any successor regulation.
      </p>
      <p>
        The calculators are <em>mathematical tools</em> that compute outputs from
        the inputs you provide using documented formulas. Returns, EMIs, tax
        liabilities, and projections shown are deterministic functions of those
        inputs — they are not predictions, recommendations, or assurances of
        future performance. Past performance does not indicate future results.
        Mutual fund investments are subject to market risks; read all scheme-related
        documents carefully.
      </p>
      <p>
        {SITE_CONFIG.name}, its operator, and its contributors do <strong>not</strong>
        recommend, endorse, or assume responsibility for any specific mutual fund,
        bank, NBFC, broker, insurance product, scheme, or investment advisor
        referenced anywhere on this site. We do not solicit business from users
        and we do not earn commissions on any financial product. Consult a
        SEBI-registered investment advisor, a chartered accountant, or a qualified
        professional before acting on any output produced here.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Not financial advice</h2>
    <p>
      The calculators on {SITE_CONFIG.name} are for personal-finance education
      only. Returns shown are computed from inputs you provide; they are not
      predictions. Verify rates, formulas, and tax treatment with your bank,
      employer, or tax professional before relying on a number.
    </p>

    <h2>Not tax advice</h2>
    <p>
      Tax and salary calculators reflect the author's reading of the Income Tax
      Act and finance bills at the time of writing. Provisions and slabs change
      every Union Budget. Verify with a chartered accountant before filing.
    </p>

    <h2>Not legal advice</h2>
    <p>
      Articles touching on regulation, KYC, or compliance reflect public
      sources at the time of writing. Verify with your own counsel before acting.
    </p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>
      We link to third-party sites (regulators, banks, fund houses, news) we
      find useful. We don't control their content, and inclusion is not an
      endorsement.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Where applicable, oriz may earn a referral fee when you sign up to a
      service via certain links. This never affects what we recommend, and any
      such links will be marked. {SITE_CONFIG.name} currently has no such
      links — calculators are independent of any product.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-head { padding-block: 3rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .eyebrow { color: var(--color-fg-muted); font-size: 0.8125rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  .eyebrow a { color: var(--color-fg-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0; }
  .meta { color: var(--color-fg-soft); font-size: 0.875rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0; }
  .prose { padding-block: 2.5rem 4rem; color: var(--color-prose); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.0625rem; }
  .prose h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .prose a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .callout {
    margin-block: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  }
  .callout h2 { margin-top: 0; }
</style>
